550 PRINT"# OF HITS IS";Q
560 G1=G1+1:G1$(G1)=Q$:H1(G1)=Q
570 IF G1=M THEN 3600
600 Q=L:GOSUB 2000:G2=G2+1:G2$(G2)=Q$
